            {"name": "Tremere", "description": "Sorcerers and scholars who built their clan on stolen power and blood magic. The Tremere are organized, hierarchical, and paranoid — and they have reason to be. Their inner council was destroyed in recent nights, and the survivors scramble to rebuild.", "bane": "Clan Curse: The Tremere's blood resonates strangely. All blood bonds with a Tremere form with only one drink instead of three.", "compulsion": "Perfectionism: The vampire cannot accept a partial success. They must retry any failed roll at least once, and cannot stop until they either succeed or physically cannot continue.", "disciplines": ["Auspex", "Blood Sorcery", "Dominate"]},
